<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center my-16">Contact me</h1>

<section class="w-3/4 mx-auto">
  <p class="mt-4">I would like to hear from you about any problems, errors, comments or suggestions you might have. Please, use the contact form below to send them to me, so I can reply to you and address your concerns in the later developments. If you are going to write about a technical problem, please, include as much technical information as possible like: your browser and operating system. What you were doing when the problem occurred? Were there any error messages displayed?</p>
  <p class="mt-4">If you want to suggest any new feature or to improve an existing one, please, describe it as clearly as possible. This product is under active development and I will consider any suggestions and improvements. Major releases are due every 3 months.</p>
  <p class="mt-4 mb-8">If you are a developer and find a bug, you can open an issue in GitHub <a href="https://github.com/Hombre2014/Portfolio-tracker/issues" class="text-dollar-split_blue cursor-pointer hover:text-dollar-triad_blue font-bold" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here.</a></p>
</section>

